com.wj.android.messageviewer.message

Class SMSMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wj.android.messageviewer.message.SMSMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMessage, java.lang.Comparable<IMessage>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MMSMessage

    public class SMSMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMessage
    The SMSMessage class represents a Short Message without a presentation definition.

    A device who receives this SMSMessage will decide how the message text is displayed.

    Author:
    Werner Jaeger
